        <updateDate>2024-06-20T13:19:21Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Housing Temperature Safety Act of 2024&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill establishes a pilot program through which the Department of Housing and Urban Development must award grants for public housing agencies and owners of certain federally assisted rental housing to install&amp;nbsp;and test temperature sensors  in dwelling units (with the written permission of tenants) for purposes of ensuring that units comply with temperature-related requirements.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;!--tinycomments|2.1|data:application/json;base64,--&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
